{
  "lesson": "WC-03-01",
  "audioMaster": "training/module03-sales/WC-03-01-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 176.431,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "This is where every ticket in the business lands.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 2.57,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "On the rail the module says Sales.",
      "startS": 3.085,
      "endS": 5.392,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "The page header says Transactions.",
      "startS": 5.924,
      "endS": 7.919,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "Same place, two names, so don't let the wording throw you.",
      "startS": 8.433,
      "endS": 11.818,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Now the numbers up top.",
      "startS": 12.24,
      "endS": 13.518,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "One tile counts every migrated ticket, past a hundred and twenty-six million.",
      "startS": 13.993,
      "endS": 18.59,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "The other three cover the last thirty days, and right now they read as a dash.",
      "startS": 19.126,
      "endS": 23.157,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "A dash means no value loaded, not zero.",
      "startS": 23.716,
      "endS": 26.478,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "First card, Ticket Volume.",
      "startS": 26.88,
      "endS": 27.553,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "It trends the last twelve months and tells you which way the line is heading.",
      "startS": 27.969,
      "endS": 28.877,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "It answers whether business is up, not what any one ticket did.",
      "startS": 29.36,
      "endS": 37.39,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Middle card, By Status.",
      "startS": 37.84,
      "endS": 38.593,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "This is the breakdown you'll lean on.",
      "startS": 38.803,
      "endS": 39.795,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "Most tickets are paid and washed.",
      "startS": 40.256,
      "endS": 44.274,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "A quarter are paid but not yet washed.",
      "startS": 44.524,
      "endS": 46.961,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "A small slice is voided.",
      "startS": 47.23,
      "endS": 50.162,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Know the normal split, and the odd day jumps out at you.",
      "startS": 50.388,
      "endS": 52.08,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Right card, Ticket Health.",
      "startS": 52.48,
      "endS": 53.978,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Three quick percentages: how many paid, how many not washed, how many voided.",
      "startS": 55.14,
      "endS": 60.3,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "It's the one-glance pulse for whatever scope you're looking at.",
      "startS": 60.805,
      "endS": 63.901,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Drop to the Search Tickets card.",
      "startS": 64.378,
      "endS": 66.046,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "With more than a hundred and twenty-six million tickets underneath, you never scroll blind.",
      "startS": 66.387,
      "endS": 69.61,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Type what you already know, or narrow it with Filters, then search.",
      "startS": 69.877,
      "endS": 71.319,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "And keep this straight: this button queries tickets;",
      "startS": 71.595,
      "endS": 75.461,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "the Search up in the header jumps between pages.",
      "startS": 75.724,
      "endS": 81.36,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Under that, the ticket list itself.",
      "startS": 81.76,
      "endS": 83.74,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "The count on the card is that same hundred-and-twenty-six-million, restated.",
      "startS": 84.487,
      "endS": 88.62,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Top-right sits Export.",
      "startS": 89.364,
      "endS": 90.886,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Find it, and leave it.",
      "startS": 91.444,
      "endS": 92.509,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "In training we locate the data-out buttons; we don't fire them.",
      "startS": 93.451,
      "endS": 97.14,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Now the columns.",
      "startS": 97.6,
      "endS": 98.659,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "Seven of them, each a way to read or sort the list:",
      "startS": 99.243,
      "endS": 100.065,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "where it rang up, its number, when, how much,",
      "startS": 100.416,
      "endS": 102.583,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "its status, how it was paid, and who it belongs to.",
      "startS": 103.252,
      "endS": 104.152,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "Every header sorts, and every row has a checkbox.",
      "startS": 104.522,
      "endS": 115.811,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "Take one row.",
      "startS": 116.361,
      "endS": 117.447,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "The ticket number is a link.",
      "startS": 117.951,
      "endS": 119.372,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "Click it and you'd open that single ticket, which is the next lesson, so leave it alone here.",
      "startS": 119.768,
      "endS": 124.643,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "And where Customer shows a dash, no customer was tied to that sale.",
      "startS": 124.898,
      "endS": 129.094,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "Glance at the pager.",
      "startS": 129.597,
      "endS": 131.066,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Twenty-five to a page, and the last page number sits just past five million.",
      "startS": 131.945,
      "endS": 137.104,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "That's the same mountain of tickets said a different way.",
      "startS": 137.656,
      "endS": 140.661,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "It's exactly why you filter before you page.",
      "startS": 141.239,
      "endS": 144.197,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "Last, the sidebar.",
      "startS": 144.64,
      "endS": 146.013,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Nine pages live under Sales, and Tickets is only the first.",
      "startS": 146.465,
      "endS": 150.286,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "The rest get their own lessons, Refund Approvals among them.",
      "startS": 150.728,
      "endS": 153.994,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "And if you trained on the old system, notice what moved:",
      "startS": 154.428,
      "endS": 157.195,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "Adjustments went to Inventory, and refund permissions still run through security levels.",
      "startS": 157.527,
      "endS": 162.21,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "That's the Tickets page.",
      "startS": 162.64,
      "endS": 164.513,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "Read health from the band and the three cards, filter before you browse,",
      "startS": 164.513,
      "endS": 168.905,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "and know the list and where Export sits.",
      "startS": 168.905,
      "endS": 171.608,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "Master this one page, and every transaction question you get starts right here.",
      "startS": 171.608,
      "endS": 176,
      "timing": "proportional"
    }
  ]
}